Wherever you are, be ALL there!
•
There is a constant battle we face daily of being PRESENT.
•
Fully focused in the moment of your current task.
•
It's not easy with all the distractions we face, but when you are FULLY focused on your family or your job or your walk outside - you are also fully FULFILLED and are GIVING your all in that moment!
•
I challenge you to TRY it today.  Be fully present as you go about your day.  Actually schedule an hour to check your phone, but leave it alone for the full hour for family dinner.
•
I think you will be surprised at how much more TIME you have laying around!
•
Again,
•
Wherever you are - BE ALL THERE! #wednesdaywisdom

Travel is our passion and after years of travelling we have seen so much beauty yet so much poverty and suffering also.  We can't change the World but we can make a difference by helping out along the way during our travels.  Cambodia has so much poverty it is heartbreaking 💔 Cambodia is a beautiful yet very conflicted place... We faced many challenges during our trip to this beautiful Country where we spent time volunteering with a local English school.  We also raised funds with our friends and family so we could purchase essential school supplies for the village kids.  We were able to directly purchase English textbooks, notepads, calculators, pencil cases, pens, pencils, sharpeners, erasers & rulers for 140 children!! We want to say a BIG THANKYOU to our friends and family who helped us raise the funds to purchase these supplies. This was a very special moment for us - a group photo with some of the Cambodian Children we helped 🙏🏽🙏🏽🇰🇭 💕 @itsa_nu_day @caracallum @ris1974 @lizmcdine @lizzijl @tash2126 #siemreap #cambodia #childrenarethefuture #volunteer #childrenoftheworld #learning #teacher #bekind #begreat #globetrotters #buddha #amazing #smile #giveback #payitforward #lifeisgreat #giving #globetrotter #behappy #kindness #travel #traveller #happy #happytravels #world #wanderlust #rtw #worldexpedition  #getonajet #seetheworldthatwemet
